{"tid":2233543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英: 若宣道小學案件7月1日後發生 教師、校長都要「以國安法伺候」","createTime":"2020-10-07T08:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T09:02:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa5f0c5ddac568cdc92328712c5d709b7ffb44a","tid":2233543,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:09:32.000Z","msg":"早前透過803基金向教局提出司法覆核的梁振英，接受葛珮帆訪問時一唱一和，梁說「教育局所謂程序要大家去估嗰啲學校、嗰啲老師係邊個，如果我係辦學團體，我係校長，教育局唔開名，我開名」。葛引述反對意見指，有關做法是否如「文化大革命」般批鬥老師，梁振英砌詞稱，「老師好似喺文化大革命咁樣批鬥係錯嘅，但係老師並唔係唔可以批評，老師犯咗事係應該除牌、譴責、勸喻」。<br />\n<br />\n梁亦指，若果有如今次宣道小學的案件是於「港版國安法」生效之後發生，就會「國安法侍候」，一再強調是「大事嚟㗎，大家唔好唔留意呢啲事。」<br />\n<br />\n梁亦將過去一年逾千名未成年人在反修例風波被捕的問題，悉數歸咎到教師身上，認為教師中有害群之馬，「係超級帶菌者必須被隔離」，教育局要公開被捕教師名單及其任職學校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/BVJISARJQNH6NC7Z2DQ5LMBIEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FBVJISARJQNH6NC7Z2DQ5LMBIEU%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=8ee20606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FBVJISARJQNH6NC7Z2DQ5LMBIEU%2F&h=66d78875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/BVJISARJQNH6NC7Z2DQ5LMBIEU/</a>"},{"pid":"d1c14ce9c27ab035129762e90c1c21c37b79d3b5","tid":2233543,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a22b9f4be4df1150d29dc6c65cd3af530199d9","tid":2233543,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"唔好扮無追溯期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},